      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is recommended only for those looking for a serious project or a source for parts. It currently has significant mechanical issues, including a rough-running engine and a transmission that requires immediate attention. The exterior shows heavy wear with noticeable rust and denting, while the interior will need a complete overhaul. It is not currently in roadworthy condition and will likely need to be towed. We are offering it at a low price for someone with the time and expertise to bring it back to life.",
